Recently, the "2024-2025 New Energy Vehicle Framework Agreement Procurement for Party and Government Agencies, Institutions and Groups in Jiangsu Province" was announced, and Tesla Model Y was included in the Jiangsu Provincial Government's new energy vehicle procurement catalog. 
It is understood that this is the first case in the country where Tesla has entered the government procurement catalog.
